dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:100,000 scale maps of Papua New Guinea, titled 'Kūchū shashin sokuzu yōzu Tōbu Papua jūmanbun no ichi-空中寫眞測圖要圖東部パプア十万分一.’ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
